-- MOVES-Deborah LaBerge joins HSBC unit as institutional sales head 
-- 
-- Wed Jul 30, 2014 03:35PM EDT
-- None



July 30 (Reuters) - HSBC Global Asset Management (USA) Inc named Deborah LaBerge as head of institutional sales, North America.

LaBerge, who will be based in New York, was previously with Scottish Widows Investment Partnership, where she was head of North America responsible for institutional sales, client service and consultant relations for seven years.